{"type": "article", "id": 63203, "title": "专为黑人设计的梳子，适用于各种发型｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2019-04-23T22:49:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 17872, "name": "Moroso"}, {"id": 58097, "name": "Natuzzi"}, {"id": 58098, "name": "Sivak+Partners"}, {"id": 22532, "name": "Patricia Urquiola"}, {"id": 58099, "name": "Yves Charles"}, {"id": 39324, "name": "Ross Lovegrove"}, {"id": 58100, "name": "Simon Skinner"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 84, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190423212312JnOa4P6LDwo7ex1y.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 14.0px; font: 12.0px Times; color: #0000e9; -webkit-text-stroke: #0000e9; min-height: 14.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #262626} span.s6 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #262626} </style>  </p><h3>Afropicks by Simon Skinner</h3><p>在今年米兰设计周的瑞典设计展 Hemma Gone Wild 上，瑞典产品设计师 Simon Skinner 展示了一组专门为黑人群体设计的梳子，整个项目被称为 Afropicks。</p><p>设计师说，非洲梳子的灵感来自黑人的头发，头发对于黑人来说，也是骄傲的象征。整个系列专门为黑人的头发制作，梳子的设计适合各种类型的黑人头发和各种发型。</p><p>“我想通过开发独特的梳齿造型，创造出一些有趣的东西，同时也抓住机会表达一些重要的事。”</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190423212421DULJtBEluSIsrxC9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190423212422YW6qStxDP5w7spOI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190423212425mcAQoOBJwCzKZdyW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190423212428bmT9cVu5UypP1xgQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190423212344w90a4jB1N82CnQAR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190423212344js4q1te75dEYAv0S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190423212345dicIFg9GHKuR7Bxt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201904232123553PGzkOig0VBp6b8o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2019/04/23/afropicks-simon-skinner-design-milan/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>bench H-01 by Sivak+Partners</h3><p>在俄罗斯港口城市敖德萨，许多路障石被放置在错误的位置，有时候会对街道和行人形成严重干扰。</p><p>对此，Sivak+Partners 工作室找到了一个聪明的解决办法：将木制长椅放置在这些圆形的石头上，不仅减少了城市中不必要的障碍，还可以为市民们带来更多的就座和休息空间。长椅底部的圆形凹槽和轻盈的木材料使其能够被牢牢地固定在球形的路障上。同时，廉价的材料也有助于城市以经济的方式取得发展。第一个长椅样本由 Cappuccino 工作室协助完成。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190423212641OolInEswS8CQKVFZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.678000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190423212518DnvrEIjtxcskB7Q6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.419830\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190423212518mO83z2jiagtHuw0v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.703750\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://sivak-partners.com/en/house-w1-2/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sivak+Partners</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Ergo Collection by Ross Lovegrove for Natuzzi</h3><p>米兰设计周期间，设计师 Ross Lovegrove 推出了与意大利家具品牌 Natuzzi 合作的首个系列家具 Ergo 。这个系列用以纪念品牌成立 60 周年，设计灵感可以追溯到品牌来源的意大利普利亚地区。</p><p>Ergo 系列包括床、躺椅、吊灯、衣物架、台灯、地毯以及镜子，整个系列标志着 Natuzzi 品牌开始专注于可持续领域的探索。</p><p>Ergo 系列完全采用具有可靠认证来源的可再生材料制作而成。对自然的贡献同时也扩展到影响卧室家具的形态。为了延续 Ross Lovegrove 最具代表性的有机设计表达方式，Ergo 系列的形态与表面独一无二的曲线与直线形态都十分光滑流畅。该系列在视觉上区分出材料与功能之间的平衡关系，同时充分反映出人们对加工产品以及产品尊重环境能力的意识。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190423212756AgGCYpx3m4sbnFy8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.709046\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190423212756bBTMrPfW38woElKu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.709046\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190423212756xUJ74Rn6mqabjDIt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190423212756PXtdUNcbAqZK6g4S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.709046\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190423212757IqcgzwZWRF3XPaGH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.491443\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190423212757Zh1SET768vdO5HuG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.709046\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201904232127587YIJVAqTEatyZ5Hh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.709046\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190423212758VT3fUEI28Qd4DiHO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.709046\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190423212759m8zPV4kj5KeJRZrC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.709046\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190423212800XOjALBbuny0HZp6S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.709046\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190423212800CIs5PzWhJ0j6Dr3t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.709046\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190423212802RMw5i4LaBGC2ZkUK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.709046\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.rosslovegrove.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ross Lovegrove</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>9.47 Table Knife by Yves Charles</h3><p>这款简单又精致的餐刀 9.47，出自米其林星级厨师 Yves Charles 之手，其设计理念是创造一款与折叠式小刀具有相同基本特征的餐刀。</p><p>Yves Charles 与 Perceval 的工匠制造商合作，生产出这款功能强大的专业刀具，可以轻松地握住和切割牛排，就好像切黄油一样容易。</p><p>每把刀都是手工制作，全柄包裹，可在切割时增加力量，以及 Sandvik 14C28N 钢刀片，具有锋利、稳定和耐腐蚀性的特点。</p><p>目前，9.47 餐刀有黑色、奶油色和黑檀木款三种选择，配有不锈钢餐叉，拉丝手柄和抛光尖齿。售价 175 美元起，<a href=\"https://www.odetothings.com/collections/all/products/9-47-table-knife\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190423212844jh5tm6nofGYc21Bk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190423212844ZK170E6oJcnMwaDQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190423212844qM0l6jbHxvcWNPd1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2019042321284464QHmXxisoV28vJI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190423212845sjFwRKEbL3SWvkmB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190423212845fjEAm82vJPY4kOM5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Gogan sofa by Patricia Urquiola for Moroso</h3><p>意大利家具品牌 Moroso 在米兰设计周期间推出新品 Gogan 沙发，操刀设计的是知名设计师 Patricia Urquiola。</p><p>Gogan 沙发样式的设计灵感，源自历经风吹雨打的自然奇石。它毛茸茸的不规则形状看起来既坚固又舒适。座椅略微向后倾斜，以增加舒适度。</p><p>整体沙发的支撑结构隐藏在沙发坐垫下方，使其外观看起来如同漂浮一般。这次选用的 bouclé 面料，是以 Moroso 纺织品历史中的一款 1970 年代面料为基础，赋予其河流岩石的外观。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190423212910diQJrPlhvEWGpMBs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201904232129109YhBJkZF1wIdNupj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201904232129105CWveIjgcxKH8hN7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190423212910G6tHNS3kUmQ9ElXK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190423212911RsOJadAHXQYM9lV2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190423212911MXGJqWLBmCDY1vFu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190423212911LGA8f9suekjP1UgV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>图片来源：Design Milk</p><p><a href=\"https://design-milk.com/patricia-urquiola-designs-a-sofa-for-moroso-inspired-by-japanese-stones/\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://design-milk.com/patricia-urquiola-designs-a-sofa-for-moroso-inspired-by-japanese-stones/</a></p>"}